 to a larger extracellular volume formed by increased glomerular filtration. Taken together, kidney morphological changes reported here for vampire bats may reflect in adults' adaptations to a monotrophic strategy.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Ribeiro, Susana Puga", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Linhares, B\u00e1rbara Silva", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sarandy, Mari\u00e1urea Matias", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fonseca, Claudio C\u00e9sar", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Puga, Luciano Carlos Heringer Porcaro", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Gonzaga, Wagner", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Sartori, Sirlene Souza Rodrigues", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Matta, S\u00e9rgio Luis Pinto Da", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Freitas, Mariella Bontempo", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/c974612e64b1e31a6fc9a1e0fe53a03f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/56d307bf503a7aae0f87398273cb8caa8164ce86cae00cdf4d1ac5189aed8db0", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/QWI3C6BQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/QWI3C6BQ", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/0829f98191a68f5305b383fa08c0cbdc!/b2486-4953", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "jou